Uncovering a gem. The Minced meat noodle with speciality sauce is surprisingly delicious, the portion is suitable for a lady to finish it all. As seen in my picture got plenty of minced meat spread on it! Chewy noodle texture too. The stall owner is quite friendly too.

Definitely going back to try other selection. Spoilt for choice in this coffee shop. ðŸ˜…
Amazing homemade food from a lovely lady. I worked in the same building and ate her La Mian all the time. Still the best I've eaten. Go try, you won't regret it!
